copy, modify, and privately distribute the Software, solely for
Qualifying Journalism Use.

You may share modifications with other Qualifying Organizations for
Qualifying Journalism Use, provided that:
  (a) You include a complete copy of this License with any distribution;
  (b) You clearly identify any modifications You have made;
  (c) You do not represent Your modified version as the official Emet
      Software.

If You are uncertain whether Your organization or use case qualifies,
You may contact the Licensor at the address below for a determination.


